deleteDups(LinkedList<T>) - Method in class LinkedList
public LinkedList deleteDuplicates(LinkedList list) { LinkedListNode n=list.getFirstNode(); HashSet set= new HashSet(); LinkedListNode previous= n; //have another cursor //start traversing the list n=n.getNext(); set.add((Integer)previous.getData()); set.add((Integer)n.getData()); while(n.getNext()!=null) { if(set.contains(n.getData())) { System.out.println(previous.getData()); previous.setNext(n.getNext());//delete the node } else { set.add((Integer)n.getData()); //add it to the set set.add((Integer)previous.getData()); } previous=previous.getNext(); n=n.getNext(); } return list; }
